Summary: Standing outside Witness saw multiple lights flying around at high speed -stoping and starting - then they formed a circle and shot off in different directions.
divs: Sighting DetailsThe Witnesses son called her outside to ask what the lights were that were flying around fast in all directions. They would stop for a second and then start up again. After a few minutes the lights moved together and formed a circle. Then they shot off in all directions until they could not see them anymore.
